name: PooChain V2
description: PooChain is a utility project on the Solana Blockchain with a governance token $POOP. $POOP can be used for staking on PooChain's launchpad poo.fun. PooChain is creating a lower starting market cap and lower bonding curve launchpad for meme tokens in partnership with some of the biggest projects on Solana. Poo.fun is live and very soon an update will be released with platform fees rewarding those engaging in the ecosystem.
